time goes by so slowly ... or so fast ... or backwards ... or forwards the third installment of our favorite wizard has him meeting a new defense of the dark arts teacher ... along with some rather scary gatekeepers as the magical world hunts for sirius black ... harry 's godfather who has escaped from the dreaded azkaban prison . meanwhile hermione discovers a way to time travel with a special locket and take more classes . it is definitley getting darker and darker ... but this third in a series sets the tone for harry 's destiny